## What is this website?

This is my personal blog/website. This is, by no means, a professional website. I might share about my diaries and some niche technical topics at the same time. Although, I would like to share about my profession too!
So, please do not think of this website as a professional website and stay tuned for my posts. This is just my hobby.

## Hello, I am Artin, and...

I'm a CSE (Computer Science & Engineering) Bachelor's student at Shiraz University. I began my program in 2023 and expect to graduate by 2027.

{{<figure src="Shiraz_University.jpg" caption="Just in case you might ask: yes, we have to climb the mountain to reach most faculties.">}}

Computer Science is my primary passion, but I am also drawn to natural sciences (specially Biology), History, and Linguistics. If I find some free time, I make sure to study about these topics, and share interesting things I find on here.

## My current focus

Currently, I am focused on 2 areas:

1) Code Generation using LLMs; 
2) Computer Vision applications in Medical Engineering.

